  <brief_title>High Risk Adult T-cell Leukemia/Lymphoma (ATLL-HR) and Allogeneic Transplant</brief_title>
  <acronym>ATLL-HR-01</acronym>
  <official_title>Observational Prospective Study, Evaluating the Standard of Care as Recommend by International Consensus With Zidovudine-Pegylated Interferon +/-Polychemotherapy in High Risk Adult-T-cell Lymphoma/Leukaemia (T-cell Lymphoma/Leukaemia) Followed by Allogeneic Transplant Among Eligible Patients Younger Than 65 Years Old</official_title>
  <sponsors>
