    <description>Zidovudine 1000mg/day : Retrovir® 250mg/day) PegINF (Pegasys®) 180μg x1 injection/week
DHAP Day 1= day 21 (3 cycles) Day 1 : Cisplatina 100 mg/m2 Day 2 and day 3 : Aracytine 2000mg/m2/day Day 1-day 4 : Dexamethasone 40mg</description>
  </arm_group>
