    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient &gt;18 years old and ≤ 75 years old, with ATLL-HR who signed informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or nursing women are not eligible; neither are women of childbearing
             potential unless using effective contraception as determined by the patient's
             physician.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
